{"tid":1466443,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"風向撚2 十一點打後追連登好撚辛苦 但五毛就係想愈黎愈少人追","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:03.000Z","uid":183798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b48ce5629aad92c9b2805b57f428ee7418b71553","tid":1466443,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"一定要追po 每晚十一點踢撚走五毛<br />\n中共啲五毛三毛 國家機器每晚十一至二都出動<br />\n就係想反完又反<br />\n<br />\n1）一係割蓆撚分化撚<br />\n2）一係扮唔割 屌在場撚<br />\n3）一係扮唔知點拆藍絲啲攻擊撚<br />\n4）一係就悲觀撚 話咩再見連登好撚辛苦呀好多分化撚<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你真係頂唔撚順 就避開十一至二 訓醒再屌三毛 <br />\n一係就硬戰三毛</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢地就係想連登仔思想混亂同埋精神疲弱 反搏唔到佢地思路就帶風向</span></span>"},{"pid":"07768244f022ff1a536c52a846e4d08d56aee918","tid":1466443,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c219f6efcf23d874ccd3935faee6b72f3f1aeee","tid":1466443,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"0204cc730086b5bb6e999a58bc9524320922308e","tid":1466443,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"ba5cde3a0e4d73e568fce4df25676e42a316bcb1","tid":1466443,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:36.000Z","msg":"推呀屌你"},{"pid":"a060a7f6ee152ad1b2f52c5cc1ca7578c509662c","tid":1466443,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"連仔封後門得唔得呀"},{"pid":"fb9cf4a102d0639e0297eda3b9c53bfad5e55ebf","tid":1466443,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"推"}]}